Combined Field: We can not change a combined field to a measure. For this we've to use a calculated field. Also combined fields are not used in IF statement 
FIXED & INCLUDE: FIXED calculation is based only on the fields before the hiphen but INCLUDE uses the fields+pills+filters in the visualization
Comment: Right click on the field on the data pane , select defaut Properties and Comment
Edit Alias of dimension for published data source is not available. In that case create duplicate field and make the changes in the calculation.
You can download the .txt file in the data source by editing the connection (left side pane). Then it will show the place in your local directory where the file is saved (may be temporary)
